    <div class="rpt-sub">28 February &#8211; 24 March 2026 (Day 25) &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Open Source Intelligence &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; IDF &middot; Times of Israel &middot; Al Jazeera &middot; NBC News &middot; CNN &middot; CBS &middot; Newsweek &middot; Bloomberg &middot; Jerusalem Post &middot; ACLED &middot; Ops.Group &middot; EASA</div>
